snippet.title: Amber Heard on DC's representation of strong women at London press junket
snippet.description:
Aside being Ireland's national treasure, in this interview Amber speaks about her character Mera and DC's representation of strong women in films, such as Mera, Queen Atlanna and Wonder Woman.
